name: alkaline phosphatase
reaction: a phosphate monoester + H2O = an alcohol + phosphate [RN:R00626]
comment: Wide specificity. Also catalyses transphosphorylations. The human placental enzyme is a zinc protein. Some enzymes hydrolyse diphosphate (cf. EC 3.6.1.1 inorganic diphosphatase)
